Package MushroomForest.Models

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Face
    Models a OBJ face
    Model
    This class encapsulates a 3D Model storing it's vertexes, faces, and normals.
    OBJLoader
    This class is OBJ loader that can parse OBJ data into a model This class is not a full OBJ loader and expects a OBJ file with Vertexes, Texture Coordinates, and Faces in (v) or (v/vt) or (v/vn/vt) format
    UnitCube
    Models a cube of unit size
    UnitCylinder
    Models a cylinder of unit size
    This class was used for testing purposes prior to OBJLoader
    UnitPlane
    Models a plane of unit size
    Vertex
    This class models a vertex
